===Noun===
{{en-noun|catebaries}}

#{{geometry}} The [[curve]] described by a flexible [[chain]] or a [[rope]] if it is supported at each end and is acted upon only by no other [[force]]s than a [[uniform]] [[gravitational]] force due to its own weight.
#{{nautical}} The curve of an [[anchor]] [[cable]] from the [[seabed]] to the [[vessel]]; it should be [[horizontal]] at the anchor so as to bury the flukes

